pass_type2 <- pass_type %>%
        filter(!patient_No %in% c(27, 44, 45, 99)) %>% # -->  
        pivot_wider(names_from = pass_type, values_from = time) %>%                      #  
        pivot_longer(cols = c("q_only", "qr", "qr_c_aid", "kiosk", "kiosk_c_aid")) %>%   #   
        na.omit() %>%
        rename(visit_time = visit, #    
               pass_type  = name, 
               pass_time  = value) %>%
        mutate(visit_to_pass_time = difftime(pass_time, visit_time, units = "secs"))     #  -
